response.overview: The 2025 Money in the Bank is an upcoming professional wrestling event produced by WWE. It will be the 16th annual Money in the Bank event and will take place on Saturday, June 7, 2025, at the Intuit Dome in Inglewood, California. The event will air via pay-per-view (PPV) and livestreaming, marking the first Money in the Bank to broadcast on Netflix, and will be held for wrestlers from the promotion's Raw and SmackDown brand divisions. The event will take place immediately after Worlds Collide.
response.title: WWE Money in the Bank 2025
